cdata.name: Signals Network
cdata.desc: The Signals Networkplatform is a decentralized platform where users can create fully customizable trading robots with no advanced technical knowledge required. Based on the Ethereum network, the SGN token allows holders to create theirown crypto-trading models based on premium indicators developed by data science community, perform complex machine learning experiments using super computer on historical data, or rent and copy-trade other successful strategies in Signals marketplace.
